ity. It is the primary defensive spell of all spellcasters in movies and roleplay games. It makes no sense at all that a highly gifted spell caster wouldn't learn a way to protect himself. If we are traveling and get snared we are dead. No pet, no root, no snare........<br>
<br>
This is something that really needs to be changed/fixed. I really do not understand what VI is afraid of. Other keeping us a tiny bit safer what is root gonna do that will be so overpowering?<br>
